&lt;p&gt;Are you an enthusiastic and motivated Band 6 midwife?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have exciting opportunities for experienced Midwives to join our committed and highly skilled team of midwives across the maternity services. The Women and Children’s division of the Trust is forward thinking and working in partnership with our local maternity systems for better births. We already have several continuity of care teams within our stand alone birth centres and we are looking to move this forward.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a team we strive to give the best evidence based care and support women to make informed choice regarding their care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting time for maternity services as we implement the recommendations of the National Transformation plans.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you wish to join our team or want further information please contact Teresa Gay (01225 821297)&lt;/p&gt;
